casebody.data:
172 A.3d 1079 IN THE MATTER OF A PETITION FOR EXPUNGEMENT OF MARTIN V. CARLUCCIO. (MARTIN V. CARLUCCIO—PETITIONER)

C-266 September Term 2017

079895 November 2, 2017

ON PETITION FOR CERTIFICATION

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court;

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-005110-15 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied, with costs.
